  <title>Watch a video</title>

  <p>You can open video files in <app>Videos</app>, in one of the
  following ways:</p>

  <list>
    <item>
      <p>Select a video from the files already displayed in the main window.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">+</gui> button in the top-left corner of
      the window and select <gui style="menuitem">Add Local Video…</gui>.
      Select the files that you want to open in the file chooser. Press
      <gui style="button">Add</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">+</gui> button in the top-left corner of
      the window and select <gui style="menuitem">Add Web Video…</gui>.
      Type or paste the address of the file you would like to open. Press
      <gui style="button">Add</gui>.</p>
    </item>
